          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Terrorism Survivors Student Loan Deferment Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends title IV (Student Assistance) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 to allow a borrower who is a victim of a terrorist attack to defer (i.e., suspend repayments on) student loans made under the Federal Family Education Loan, Federal Direct Loan, and Federal Perkins Loan programs. </p>]]></text>
